longBusinessSummary: ISM International Inc. develops and sells green energy products and organic non-toxic products in Canada. The company offers its products under the MyGirl, Superwipes, SwatBra, GotchaGps, and BioSolvant trademarks. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Clearwater, Florida.
